OL,3,CWhy Trump's peace deal with Iran has
OL,4,Cleft Israel feeling betrayed
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump says he
OL,7,Fagreed to a peace deal with Iran
OL,8,Fbecause he didn't want to become
OL,9,Fanother Herbert Hoover and preside
OL,10,Fover a second Great Depression.
OL,12,FHis critics say that he's emulated
OL,13,FWoodrow Wilson instead, by signing
OL,14,Fanother terrible treaty in Versailles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
