OL,3,CWhy Trump's peace deal with Iran has
OL,4,Cleft Israel feeling betrayed
OL,6,FShortly after the war began, Trump
OL,7,Fsaid he would settle for nothing less
OL,8,Fthan Iran's unconditional surrender.
OL,9,FBut when it came to it, Tehran didn't
OL,10,Fhave to surrender very much to
OL,11,Fpersuade him to sign on the dotted
OL,12,Fline.
OL,14,FIn the same way that America's
OL,15,FEuropean allies weren't consulted
OL,16,Fbefore the war began, Israel wasn't
OL,17,Fconsulted about the way it would end.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
