OL,3,CWhy Trump's peace deal with Iran has
OL,4,Cleft Israel feeling betrayed
OL,6,FAt the outset, Israel and the United
OL,7,FStates looked like equal partners
OL,8,Fwaging war to achieve shared goals -
OL,9,Fthe conditions for regime change in
OL,10,FTehran; the destruction of Iran's
OL,11,Fnuclear and ballistic missiles
OL,12,Fprogrammes and the end of Iranian
OL,13,Fsupport for its regional proxies like
OL,14,Fthe Houthis and Hezbollah.
OL,16,FNot only have none of these aims been
OL,17,Fachieved, but some are being reversed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
