OL,3,CWhy Trump's peace deal with Iran has
OL,4,Cleft Israel feeling betrayed
OL,6,FThe United States will allow Iran to
OL,7,Facquire more ballistic missiles under
OL,8,Fthe agreement. Trump's logic appears
OL,9,Fto be that other countries in the
OL,10,Fregion, like Saudi Arabia, will have
OL,11,Fthem so fair's fair.
OL,13,FAs well as that, both America and Iran
OL,14,Fagree "not to interfere in each
OL,15,Fother's internal affairs". This can
OL,16,Fonly mean that Washington is
OL,17,Fabandoning efforts to create the
OL,18,Fconditions for regime change.
OL,26,@vD@GOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
