OL,3,CWhy Trump's peace deal with Iran has
OL,4,Cleft Israel feeling betrayed
OL,6,FNot surprisingly, most Israelis are
OL,7,Fhorrified by the deal and regard it as
OL,8,Fcapitulation.
OL,10,FAnd they fear that Washington will not
OL,11,Ftry to inhibit Israel when it comes to
OL,12,Fthe way the IDF combats this country's
OL,13,Fenemies.
OL,15,FThe deal very much includes a
OL,16,Fceasefire in Lebanon and commits
OL,17,FAmerica and Iran to "ensuring the
OL,18,Fterritorial integrity and sovereignty
OL,19,Fof Lebanon".
OL,26,@yD@UOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
