OL,3,CWhy Trump's peace deal with Iran has
OL,4,Cleft Israel feeling betrayed
OL,6,FBut Hezbollah and Israel are still at
OL,7,Fwar. Right now, the Israeli government
OL,8,Fis resisting US pressure to withdraw
OL,9,Ffrom south Lebanon, which will
OL,10,Fpresumably be a Hezbollah requisite
OL,11,Ffor ceasing fire.
OL,13,FDuring his news conference at the G7,
OL,14,FTrump said he expected to welcome
OL,15,FPresident Aoun of Lebanon to
OL,16,FWashington next week or the week after.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
