OL,3,CWhy Trump's peace deal with Iran has
OL,4,Cleft Israel feeling betrayed
OL,6,FIt's likely the Americans will want
OL,7,Fthe Israeli Prime Minister there as
OL,8,Fwell to sign what would be an historic
OL,9,FIsrael-Lebanon peace agreement that
OL,10,Fincludes a Lebanese commitment to
OL,11,Fcombat Hezbollah with US support.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FSuch a deal would provide Benjamin
OL,19,FNetanyahu with some diplomatic cover
OL,20,Fto order an IDF withdrawal from
OL,21,FLebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
