OL,3,CWhy Trump's peace deal with Iran has
OL,4,Cleft Israel feeling betrayed
OL,6,FRight now, the Israeli leader must be
OL,7,Fwondering how relations with "Israel's
OL,8,Fbest friend ever in the White House"
OL,9,Fhave deteriorated so far so fast.
OL,11,FHe can't know if Trump loves him or
OL,12,Floathes him.
OL,14,FIn between heaping praise, the US
OL,15,FPresident has recently cast doubt on
OL,16,Fwhether Netanyahu will stand in the
OL,17,Fupcoming election, accused him of
OL,18,Fhaving no f***ing judgement, of being
OL,19,Fungrateful and a "very difficult guy".
