OL,3,CWhy Trump's peace deal with Iran has
OL,4,Cleft Israel feeling betrayed
OL,6,FSo far, the Israeli Prime Minister has
OL,7,Fresisted public criticism of his
OL,8,Ferstwhile bestie. After all, he's
OL,9,Fburnt his bridges with most other
OL,10,Fworld leaders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
